  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    play.Play.application()
    inject the Application instead. Deprecated since 2.5.0.
    play.i18n.Lang.availables()
    Please use Lang.availables(app), since 2.5.0
    play.mvc.Results.badRequest(JsonNode, String)
    As of 2.6.0, use badRequest(JsonNode, JsonEncoding)
    play.Application.configuration()
    play.inject.guice.GuiceBuilder.configure(Configuration)
    play.libs.crypto.CSRFTokenSigner.constantTimeEquals(String, String)
    since 2.6.0. Use java.security.MessageDigest.isEqual over this method.
    play.libs.crypto.DefaultCSRFTokenSigner.constantTimeEquals(String, String)
    play.http.HttpRequestHandler.createAction(Http.Request, Method)
    Use ActionCreator instead.
    play.mvc.Results.created(JsonNode, String)
    As of 2.6.0, use created(JsonNode, JsonEncoding)
    play.libs.concurrent.HttpExecution.defaultContext()
    Since 2.6.0, use HttpExecutionContext.current() from an action, or use HttpExecution.fromThread(ExecutionContext) with a dependency injected ExecutionContext or ActorSystem directly.
    play.libs.Files.TemporaryFile.file()
    Use path() over file().
    play.mvc.Results.forbidden(JsonNode, String)
    As of 2.6.0, use forbidden(JsonNode, JsonEncoding)
    play.cache.DefaultSyncCacheApi.getOrElse(String, Callable<T>)
    Use getOrElseUpdate instead (2.6.0)
    play.cache.DefaultSyncCacheApi.getOrElse(String, Callable<T>, int)
    Use getOrElseUpdate instead (2.6.0)
    play.libs.Classpath.getReflectionsConfiguration(String, ClassLoader)
    Deprecated as of 2.6.0
    play.libs.Classpath.getTypes(Application, String)
    Deprecated as of 2.6.0
    play.libs.Classpath.getTypes(Environment, String)
    Deprecated as of 2.6.0
    play.libs.Classpath.getTypesAnnotatedWith(Application, String, Class<? extends Annotation>)
    Deprecated as of 2.6.0
    play.libs.Classpath.getTypesAnnotatedWith(Environment, String, Class<? extends Annotation>)
    Deprecated as of 2.6.0
    play.ApplicationLoader.Context.initialConfiguration()
    play.mvc.Results.internalServerError(JsonNode, String)
    As of 2.6.0, use internalServerError(JsonNode, JsonEncoding)
    play.inject.guice.GuiceApplicationBuilder.load(BiFunction<Environment, Configuration, List<GuiceableModule>>)
    Use withModuleLoader instead
    play.inject.guice.GuiceApplicationBuilder.loadConfig(Configuration)
    Use loadConfig(Config
    play.inject.guice.GuiceApplicationBuilder.loadConfig(Function<Environment, Configuration>)
    Use withConfigLoader
    play.mvc.Results.notFound(JsonNode, String)
    As of 2.6.0, use notFound(JsonNode, JsonEncoding
    play.mvc.Results.ok(JsonNode, String)
    As of 2.6.0, use ok(JsonNode, JsonEncoding)
    play.data.format.Formatters.parse(Field, String, Class<T>)
    As of 2.6.0, use Formatters.parse(Field, String) instead
    play.mvc.Results.paymentRequired(JsonNode, JsonEncoding)
    As of 2.6.0, use paymentRequired(JsonNode, JsonEncoding)
    play.i18n.Lang.preferred(List<Lang>)
    Please use preferred(app, langs). Deprecated since 2.5.0.
    play.mvc.StatusHeader.sendJson(JsonNode, String)
    As of 2.6.0, use sendJson(JsonNode, JsonEncoding)
    play.libs.ws.WSRequest.setBody(InputStream)
    use WSRequest.setBody(Source) instead.
    play.mvc.Http.Response.setContentType(String)
    noop. Use Result.as(String) instead.
    play.mvc.Http.Response.setCookie(String, String, Integer, String, String, boolean, boolean)
    Use Http.Response.setCookie(Http.Cookie) instead.
    play.mvc.Results.status(int, JsonNode, String)
    As of 2.6.0, use status(int, JsonNode, JsonEncoding)
    play.mvc.Http.RequestBuilder.tag(String, String)
    Use attr(key, value) instead.
    play.mvc.Http.RequestHeader.tags()
    Use attr, withAttr, etc.
    play.mvc.Http.RequestBuilder.tags()
    Use typed attributes, i.e. attrs(), instead.
    play.mvc.Http.RequestBuilder.tags(Map<String, String>)
    Use attrs(...) instead.
    play.mvc.Http.Request.username()
    As of release 2.6, use attrs.get(Security.USERNAME) or attrs.getOptional(Security.USERNAME).
    play.mvc.Http.RequestBuilder.username()
    Use attrs().get(Security.USERNAME) or attrs().getOptional(Security.USERNAME) instead.
    play.mvc.Http.RequestBuilder.username(String)
    Use attr(Security.USERNAME, username) instead.
    play.ApplicationLoader.Context.withConfiguration(Configuration)
    play.mvc.Http.CookieBuilder.withMaxAge(Integer)
    As of 2.6.0, use withMaxAge(Duration) instead.
    play.mvc.Http.Request.withUsername(String)
    As of release 2.6, use req.withAttrs(req.attrs().put(Security.USERNAME, username)).
    play.http.ActionCreator.wrapAction(Action)
    Use createAction and set play.http.actionComposition.executeActionCreatorActionFirst = true
    play.http.HttpRequestHandler.wrapAction(Action)
    Use ActionCreator instead.
